\v 7 Kodwa ulwazi\x + 10.15. 8.7,10. Roma 15.14. Roma 14.14,22.\x* kalukho kubo bonke; kanti abanye belesazela\x + 10.25,27,29.\x* sesithombe kuze kube khathesi bayakudla njengokuhlatshelwe isithombe\x + 8.4,7,10. Seb. 15.29.\x*, lesazela sabo esibuthakathaka singcoliswa\x + Roma 14.14,23.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa ukudla\x + Roma 14.17.\x* kakusisondezi kuNkulunkulu; ngoba kungesikuthi nxa sisidla, silenzuzo; njalo kungesikuthi nxa singadli, silokulahlekelwa.
