\v 10 Ngoba uba umuntu\x + 10.28.\x* ekubona wena ololwazi\x + 10.15. 8.7,10. Roma 15.14. Roma 14.14,22.\x* uhlezi ekudleni ethempelini lesithombe, isazela\x + 10.25,27,29.\x* salowo obuthakathaka kasiyikuqiniswa\f + \fk ukuqiniswa: \fl kumbe, \fq ukwakhiwa.\f* yini ukuthi adle izinto ezihlatshelwe izithombe?
\v 11 Ngenxa yolwazi lwakho\x + 10.28.\x* lomzalwane obuthakathaka\x + 8.11. Roma 14.1.\x* uzabhubha yini, amfelayo uKristu\x + Roma 14.15.\x*?
\v 12 Kodwa uba lisona\x + Mat. 25.40,45.\x* ngokunjalo kubazalwane, lilimaza isazela sabo esibuthakathaka, liyona kuKristu.
